style="background: #fcc" | {{{1|No}}}<noinclude> ---- This template is designed to be used in a table to make a cell with "No" in that cell, with a red background.
Example: {|style="font-size: 85%; text-align: center;" class="wikitable" |Example: |{{no}} |}
== See also == * [[Template:Yes]] </noinclude>

